# === Secrets: NEVER commit real config that contains credentials ===
# 真实配置文件（含数据库密码 / JWT 密钥）一律忽略，只提交 -example 模板
ruoyi-admin/src/main/resources/application.yml
ruoyi-admin/src/main/resources/application-druid.yml
ruoyi-admin/src/main/resources/application-prod.yml
ruoyi-admin/src/main/resources/application-dev.yml

# 保留脱敏后的示例模板（可安全入库）
!ruoyi-admin/src/main/resources/application-example.yml
!ruoyi-admin/src/main/resources/application-druid-example.yml

# 本地上传目录（Windows / Linux 路径）
